original: Joabson, Knut Henning, kommunalborgmästare, Troldhättan, f. 3/3/99 i Hovmantorp, Kronob. 1., av trävaru-handl. Axel J. o. Kristina Andersson. G. 30 m. Viola Lücklig. Barn: Lars Henning f. 31, Ann-Christine 35. — Stud:ex. i Växjö 20, jur. kand. i Lund 26. Andre rådm. i 0’skarshamn 30, tf. förste rådm. där 33-37, komm:-borgmäst. i Trollhättan sed. 38. Huv:-man i Trollhättans Sparbank, led. av styr. f. TroiHhättans samrealsk. o. f. västra distr. dövstum’skolor.
translated: Joabson, Knut Henning, municipal mayor, Troldhättan, b. 3/3/99 in Hovmantorp, Kronoberg County, 1st child of timber merchant Axel J. and Kristina Andersson. Married on 30 in m. Viola Lücklig. Children: Lars Henning b. 31, Ann-Christine b. 35. — Studied:ex. in Växjö in 20, law degree in Lund in 26. Second judge in Oskarshamn in 30, acting first judge there from 33-37, municipal mayor in Trollhättan since 38. Principal of Trollhättans Savings Bank, board member of Trollhättan Secondary School and the Western District Deaf and Dumb Schools.

boardMember.name: Western District Deaf and Dumb Schools
